WEBVTT

00:15:59.530 --> 00:16:01.877
(Ả rập) Omer anh tôi

00:16:02.743 --> 00:16:05.662
em sẽ luôn yêu anh

00:16:06.347 --> 00:16:08.252
(Tiếng anh) Omer anh tôi

00:16:08.252 --> 00:16:11.252
em sẽ luôn yêu anh.

00:16:11.252 --> 00:16:12.252
Trước lần khai quật đầu tiên của tôi

00:16:12.252 --> 00:16:13.503
tại Ai Cập,

00:16:13.503 --> 00:16:14.433
cố vấn của tôi, vị giáo sư nổi tiếng

00:16:14.453 --> 00:16:15.733
nghiên cứu về Ai Cập,

00:16:15.733 --> 00:16:17.221
ông William Kelley Simpson

00:16:17.221 --> 00:16:18.516
gọi tôi tới văn phòng ông,

00:16:19.049 --> 00:16:22.406
đưa tôi tấm séc 2000 đô

00:16:22.430 --> 00:16:25.104
rồi nói: "Nó sẽ trả kinh phí của em

00:16:25.128 --> 00:16:26.128
hãy có cuộc phiêu lưu vẻ vang

00:16:26.128 --> 00:16:27.728
vào mùa hè này,

00:16:27.728 --> 00:16:29.741
sẽ có một ngày em làm điều ấy

00:16:29.741 --> 00:16:32.161
cho người nào đó"